{"tid":2225045,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15人涉暴動 官：不知檢控基礎","createTime":"2020-10-01T04:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T06:15:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b53a7804903dc1d179335027a832e724f3a8c8ab","tid":2225045,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:30:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/ZX2QO63TIJAALPWAYQ6PUHTGFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FZX2QO63TIJAALPWAYQ6PUHTGFQ%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2FolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=743d68ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FZX2QO63TIJAALPWAYQ6PUHTGFQ%2F&h=4162e449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/ZX2QO63TIJAALPWAYQ6PUHTGFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n15人涉暴動 官：不知檢控基礎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IQC98d4pKAxd-qWHxIUHE0lzmNg=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MKW43K6NARA5XBROFDY2ERYULM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIQC98d4pKAxd-qWHxIUHE0lzmNg%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMKW43K6NARA5XBROFDY2ERYULM.jpg&h=10b2ac51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前學民思潮發言人黃子悅被控參與暴動，昨在區院提訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【理大圍城案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11月警方圍堵理工大學，大批市民為聲援校內抗爭者，在油麻地一帶與警方爆發衝突，事後213人被控暴動。其中包括前學民思潮發言人黃子悅在內的15名被告，昨首度在區域法院提訊。首席法官高勁修直言，控方案情大篇幅提及事發前兩日發生何事，但針對被告的指控卻只得一句，「淨係話佢哋參與暴動」，不清楚「檢控基礎係乜嘢」，要求控方於下次聆訊前釐清。<br />\n<br />\n昨共有54名被告分三案提訊，控方稱已準備好答辯，惟被告要求押後答辯待申請法援，獲法庭批准。<br />\n<br />\n首案牽涉黃子悅與14名被告，控罪指他們於去年11月18日在油麻地彌敦道近窩打老道交界參與暴動。法官高勁修主動提及，控方案情主要講述去年11月17日及18日發生的事件，「就呢15個被告實際做咗乜嘢，似乎得一句有關，淨係話佢哋參與暴動」。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促控方下次聆訊前釐清<br />\n<br />\n法官建議控方及早釐清檢控基礎，尤其整件事件涉及213名被告；若遲遲未決，辯方實難以參與討論，要求控方於下次聆訊前，向辯方交代檢控基礎、相關片段針對哪位被告，及對被告分拆或合併審訊有何建議。黃一案押後至下月20日，另外兩案則分別押後至12月4及11日。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC736、751、755/20"},{"pid":"a0a28f7e82759627f4a521b775161fb0a92a74da","tid":2225045,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"又多啲時間作故仔"},{"pid":"c0242a69b4da66344cc22c518bebfa47b9801d5c","tid":2225045,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"如果你已經唔記得當初喺為咩而行出嚟，當初喺為咩而憤怒，就入嚟睇下條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【自由之歌】有個香港人無收錢整咗條咁嘅片出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2224648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2224648</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3588bdfec19a112a01a249d72452b9a6cfb07df4","tid":2225045,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f95a569e071026b39b82a505d7ce2df54541c5","tid":2225045,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"個官有問題<br />\n成家外國護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884dfdec5f53c26ff809cce5f72a54e24cf882d7","tid":2225045,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73f95a569e071026b39b82a505d7ce2df54541c5","tid":2225045,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"個官有問題<br />\n成家外國護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"佢已經係區域法院首席法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7aeb8634710be82b655599116ad826d4f4ab1d","tid":2225045,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/